hub (1.6.1-1) lucid; urgency=low

  * Update homepage in debian/control
  * New upstream release (v1.6.1):
    - `git push remote1,remote2` without branch name pushes the current branch
    - Fix `browse` command for current repo with no tracking setup
    - Preserve global flags to git
    - Add cross-platform command detection and browser launcher

 -- Sebastian Boehm <sebastian@sometimesfood.org>  Wed, 25 May 2011 18:52:17 +0200

